IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. SIGNAL-HANDLER-ERROR-TERMINATES.

DATA DIVISION.
01 TARGET-FIELD PICTURE IS X(30).
01 HANDLER-TARGET PICTURE IS X(30).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MOVE "MISSING-TARGET" TO TARGET-FIELD
MOVE "BAD-IN-HANDLER" TO HANDLER-TARGET
SIGNAL HANDLER ON ERROR
GO TO TARGET-FIELD.

HANDLER.
GO TO HANDLER-TARGET.
